</p>

<p corresp='TTP32498409P1' xml:id='OTP32498409P1'>The State of Mississippi<lb/>
<rs ref='#S63243'>Wayne County</rs><hr/>
</p>

<p corresp='TTP32498409P2' xml:id='OTP32498409P2'>We <rs ref='#S25027308'>P. H. Napier</rs> <rs ref='#S32003247'>Probate</rs> <rs ref='#S63934'>Judge</rs> <rs ref='#S84069'>Angus Taylor</rs> <rs ref='#S95578'>Sheriff</rs> and <rs ref='#S25012736'>W. S. Davis</rs> <rs ref='#S50807'>Clerk</rs> of the <rs ref='#S70054'>Circuit</rs> and <rs ref='#S55586'>Pro-bate Courts</rs> of said County, do hereby certify upon our honor that, <rs ref='#S32047402'>Isham C Moody</rs> is a resident Citizen of the County of Wayne aforesaid and has been for about one year last past, and that he is a sober and reliable man, and one in our opinion, well qualified to discharge the duties of a <rs ref='#S32031022'><hi rend='underline'>dispenser</hi> of spirituous liquors</rs> for medical purposes.
</p>

<p corresp='TTP32498409P3' xml:id='OTP32498409P3'>Apl 26<add place='above'>th</add> A. D. 1864.
</p>

<p corresp='TTP32498409P4' xml:id='OTP32498409P4'>P. H. Napier Probate Judge<lb/>
A Taylor Sheriff<lb/>
W. S. Davis Clerk Cir <rs ref='#S63395'>Court</rs><lb/>
W S Davis Clerk Pro. Court
</p>

<p corresp='TTP32498409P5' xml:id='OTP32498409P5'>[seal]
</p>

<p corresp='TTP32498409P6' xml:id='OTP32498409P6'>[seal] 
